2)Write a command that removes all orders from customer Clemens from the Orders table.

kd4_rahul_83497@localhost>delete from ORDERS where Cnum =any(select Cnum from CUSTOMERS where Cname ='Clemens');
Query OK, 2 rows affected (0.02 sec)

kd4_rahul_83497@localhost>select * from ORDERS;

