3)Write a command that increases the rating of all customers in Rome by 100.

kd4_rahul_83497@localhost>select City ,Rating+100 from CUSTOMERS where City='Rome';
+------+------------+
| City | Rating+100 |
+------+------------+
| Rome |        300 |
| Rome |        200 |
+------+------------+
2 rows in set (0.00 sec)


